{"hash":"c172d95f3caedc458b15c41bd34a3ceddae884e7","data":{"metadata":{"siteName":"只是玩玩 | JUST FUN","siteDescription":"/gridsome-blog"},"post":{"id":"63158312cf533d1c2cf29a79","title":"关于《平凡之路》和《Promise》","content":"<!--kg-card-begin: markdown--><p>最近到处都是韩寒《后会无期》的宣传，现在的作家越来越不老实了，跨界都跨到电影界了，不过想想也是——低成本高收益的先列太多。都想过来捞一笔，今天无意间看到有人说朴树的平凡之路有抄袭《Promise》，这是一首寂静岭2里面的歌曲。我听了一下，伴奏的确是很像。不过是不是抄袭就仁者见仁智者见智了。</p>\n<p><embed height=\"33\" invokeurls=\"false\" src=\"http://www.xiami.com/widget/0_1773346501/singlePlayer.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"257\" wmode=\"transparent\"></p>\n<p><embed height=\"33\" invokeurls=\"false\" src=\"http://www.xiami.com/widget/0_3061532/singlePlayer.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"257\" wmode=\"transparent\"></p>\n<!--kg-card-end: markdown-->","date":"23 July 2014","path":"on-the-road-of-ordinary-and-the-promise"}},"context":{}}